  {:at :liveness-not-re-derivability
   :wanted "the substrate's deliverables must be QUERYABLE from the store, not merely re-derivable by re-running a script (completion-rot: substrate-1 claimed 1,524+ edges, 0 live)"
   :discharged-by "phase-4 multi-watcher (fs-event → hyperedge within ~5s debounce, SHA-256 no-op skip, typed watcher-event on delete/rename); PARTIAL for commits (E-live-means-live: manual-batch)"}]

